<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.7">
<l>taraṅkanīr pēciṉun taṇmati kāyiṉum</l>
<l>iraṅkumō vettaṉai nāḷirun teḷkiṉāḷ</l>
<l>turaṅkamvāy kīṇṭukan tāṉatu toṉmaiyūr</l>
<l>araṅkamē yeṉpa tivaḷtaṉak kācaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If the roiling waters roar and if cool moonbeams burn,</l>
<l>Won’t she weep? For how many days has she suffered?</l>
<l>The ancient city of Araṅkam of him who was satisfied</l>
<l>Having split the horse’s mouth, that is her only desire.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
